                    <li>Modern Bathrooms: Enjoy a spa-like experience with our modern, well-appointed bathrooms.</li>
                    <li>Cozy Living Spaces: Relax in our inviting living areas with fireplaces, perfect for chilly nights.</li>
                    <li>Fully-Equipped Kitchens: Prepare your favorite meals in our fully-stocked kitchens.</li>
                    <li>Private Outdoor Spaces: Take in the stunning views from your private deck or patio.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Activities and Amenities</h3>
                <p>At Cozy Cabin, there’s no shortage of activities to keep you entertained:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Outdoor Adventures: Hiking, fishing, kayaking, and more.</li>
                    <li>Wellness Retreats: Yoga sessions, spa treatments, and wellness workshops.</li>
                    <li>Seasonal Activities: Skiing in winter, wildflower walks in spring, and autumn leaf-peeping.</li>
                    <li>Local Excursions: Explore nearby attractions, including charming mountain towns and cultural landmarks.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
